I don't want him around.

01:58.159 --> 01:59.159
He wouldn't be around.

01:59.227 --> 02:00.461
It's an honorary position.

02:00.529 --> 02:01.662
I don't give a shit.

02:01.730 --> 02:03.530
Well, I think you do,

02:03.598 --> 02:05.365
