since I left,

02:05.433 --> 02:07.800
which means it's you
who's been dealing in bad faith.

02:07.868 --> 02:10.002
Well, now that you've got
a grasp on what's happened

02:10.070 --> 02:11.570
in the goddamn interim,

02:11.638 --> 02:13.305
what are you
gonna do about it?

02:13.373 --> 02:14.973
Because he's not getting
that title.

02:15.041 --> 02:18.344
Well, let me make sure
I understand this, okay?

02:18.411 --> 02:20.946
We negotiated a deal that
gave you everything you wanted,

02:21.014 --> 02:23.750
Mr. Cooper signed it,
and now you won't close

02:23.817 --> 02:25.618
