the last shred of his dignity?

02:25.686 --> 02:27.788
- Bingo.
- Well, that's not gonna happen.

02:27.855 --> 02:30.090
- And why the hell not?
- Because I like Mr. Cooper,

02:30.158 --> 02:32.426
and my firm doesn't operate
in bad faith.

02:32.494 --> 02:35.329
Oh.
I see how it is.

02:35.397 --> 02:36.564
Instead of working Cooper,

02:36.632 --> 02:38.833
you're working me.

02:38.901 --> 02:41.235
Well, why don't you take
your pansy attitude

02:41.303 --> 02:43.838
back in there
and make him sign my deal?

02:43.906 --> 02:45.573
Or I'll pay someone else
your money

02:45.641 --> 02:48.109
to do it for me.
First of all, Gerald,

02:48.177 --> 02:49.944
if you think
anyone's gonna touch this deal

02:50.011 --> 02:52.880
after your bad faith,
you're mistaken.

02:52.947 --> 02:56.316
Second, the way
our agreement works is,

02:56.384 --> 02:57.951
the minute Cooper
signed the deal

02:58.019 --> 02:59.519
which gave you everything
you wanted,

02:59.587 --> 03:02.556
our fee was due and payable,
which is why at 7:30

03:02.623 --> 03:05.626
I received confirmation
of a wire transfer

03:05.694 --> 03:08.729
from escrow indicating payment
in full.

03:15.104 --> 03:16.605
So I'd say
the ball's in your court,

03:16.673 --> 03:19.207
but the truth is
your balls are in my fist.

03:19.275 --> 03:22.677
Now I apologize if that image
is too pansy for you,

03:22.745 --> 03:24.112
but I'm comfortable enough
with my manhood

03:24.179 --> 03:25.446
to put it out there.

03:25.514 --> 03:27.081
Now get your ass in there

03:27.149 --> 03:30.184
and close the goddamn deal.

03:30.252 --> 03:31.952
You gonna let him talk to me
like this?

03:32.019 --> 03:34.354
