03:48.002 --> 03:50.971
We got paid
before Gerald signed the deal?

03:51.038 --> 03:52.405
What are you talking about?
This is a memo

03:52.473 --> 03:54.074
about some fire drill
on Tuesday.

03:54.142 --> 03:55.742
