to stop getting stoned.

06:09.144 --> 06:10.377
I've got to get
my act together.

06:10.445 --> 06:11.912
Dude, look at me.

06:11.980 --> 06:14.415
You can burn bud
and still be a success.

06:14.483 --> 06:16.084
