07:16.043 --> 07:17.743
Hi, sweetie.

07:17.811 --> 07:19.212
What a pleasant surprise.

07:19.280 --> 07:21.114
I'm so glad you stopped by.
Yeah.

07:21.182 --> 07:22.349
We're in the middle
of something.

07:22.416 --> 07:24.384
What are you
in the middle of?

07:24.452 --> 07:26.253
Trevor's trying
to set me up.

07:26.321 --> 07:27.621
That's terrific.

07:27.689 --> 07:29.457
Who's the lucky girl?

07:29.524 --> 07:31.326
