off Trevor,

07:34.797 --> 07:35.798
and you'll pick up
writing code

07:35.865 --> 07:37.767
like you do everything else.

07:37.834 --> 07:39.268
All right.
I got to go.

07:39.336 --> 07:41.003
I got go get up early
to see my grandmother

07:41.070 --> 07:42.104
and pay them another month.

07:42.172 --> 07:43.672
Oh.

07:45.574 --> 07:46.574
- Good night.
- Bye.

07:49.378 --> 07:52.146
How did you know Gerald
wouldn't look at that memo?

07:52.213 --> 07:54.214
Because a charging bull
always looks at the red cape,

07:54.282 --> 07:55.749
not at the man
with the sword.

07:55.816 --> 07:57.884
By the way,
I've set up a meeting

07:57.951 --> 08:00.086
for you and John Dockery
next week.

08:00.154 --> 08:01.588
Dockery?
He's Skadden's biggest client.

08:01.655 --> 08:02.656
Not anymore.

08:02.723 --> 08:04.491
He's looking around.

08:04.559 --> 08:05.826
He plays tennis.
I want you to close him.

08:05.894 --> 08:07.261
Consider it done.

08:07.329 --> 08:10.298
Then you are
officially dismissed

08:10.366 --> 08:12.167
for the evening.

08:12.234 --> 08:13.835
Cheers.

08:13.903 --> 08:14.903
Well, you two seem
to be celebrating something.

08:14.971 --> 08:17.239
Mm-hmm.
We are.

08:17.307 --> 08:18.808
In fact, you are looking

08:18.876 --> 08:20.109
at the best closer
this city has ever seen.

08:20.177 --> 08:21.411
Closer, huh?

08:21.478 --> 08:22.811
Baseball?
Attorney.

08:22.879 --> 08:24.313
I close situations.

08:24.381 --> 08:26.216
Hmm.
So you only care about money?

08:26.283 --> 08:28.051
The truth is,
I do it for the children.

08:29.988 --> 08:31.555
I'm Lisa.

08:31.623 --> 08:32.857
Harvey.

08:32.924 --> 08:35.927
Lisa, I don't normally do this,

08:35.995 --> 08:37.595
but since we are celebrating,

08:37.663 --> 08:39.496
what time do you get off
tonight?

08:39.565 --> 08:41.499
I'm glad you asked.

08:41.567 --> 08:45.804
I get off at ten past
"I'm never going out with you."

08:48.375 --> 08:52.477
I guess you're not the best
closer this city's ever seen.

08:55.815 --> 09:03.588
♪ ♪

09:06.426 --> 09:07.926
Good morning.

09:07.994 --> 09:09.561
Lisa, this was lovely,

09:09.629 --> 09:11.330
but I'm afraid
you have to go.

09:11.398 --> 09:13.065
- Aw.
- I hate to miss a workout,

09:13.133 --> 09:15.367
and I really need
to be in the office by 7:30.

09:15.435 --> 09:17.636
I can make you breakfast?

09:17.704 --> 09:19.138
