off my stomach.

09:19.205 --> 09:20.405
I guess if I skip the gym,

09:20.473 --> 09:22.374
I can still get in by 9:00.

09:33.953 --> 09:36.855
I hear someone's
not taking their pills.

09:36.923 --> 09:39.524
