with that stuff.

10:06.883 --> 10:08.116
What stuff?

10:08.184 --> 10:10.685
I may be old,

10:10.753 --> 10:12.621
but I'm not an idiot.

10:12.689 --> 10:14.824
I know life has been hard
for you,

10:14.891 --> 10:16.325
but you're not a kid anymore,

10:16.393 --> 10:18.094
and I want you to promise

10:18.162 --> 10:20.497
you're gonna start living up
to your potential.

10:26.037 --> 10:27.771
