10:31.076 --> 10:33.044
I'm not saying that I haven't
been charmed by Harvey,

10:33.112 --> 10:34.879
but it's just so patronizing

10:34.947 --> 10:36.615
when you say
that he can handle those things

10:36.682 --> 10:38.149
and, "Louis,
you can only handle this."

10:38.217 --> 10:40.051
Jessica, I could have handled
Gerald Tate.

10:40.118 --> 10:41.385
And I told you
I disagree.

10:41.453 --> 10:43.287
- Why?
- Because when you put

10:43.355 --> 10:44.622
two bullies
in the same room together,

10:44.689 --> 10:46.623
things generally
don't go so well.

10:46.691 --> 10:48.091
It's 9:30.
Nice of you to show up

10:48.159 --> 10:49.959
two hours after we open
for business.

10:50.027 --> 10:51.994
And I see that you're also
trying to look like a pimp.

10:52.062 --> 10:54.863
My bad, Louis.
I was out late last night.

10:54.931 --> 10:55.797
