11:54.192 --> 11:57.061
Louis, this is how it is.

11:57.129 --> 12:00.398
All right,
now you two make nice.

12:00.465 --> 12:02.900
Louis, I apologize.
I was out of line.

12:02.968 --> 12:06.670
