14:38.390 --> 14:40.491
Great. Thanks.

14:40.559 --> 14:43.528
Donna, we're gonna need
to streamline this.

14:43.596 --> 14:45.363
Give each guy a hard time.

14:45.431 --> 14:46.932
Before you send them back,

14:47.000 --> 14:48.533
give me a wink
if they say something clever.

14:48.601 --> 14:50.269
Cool?
Okay.

14:50.336 --> 14:51.336
